hadiths[33]{hadithnumber,text}:
2573,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din jahannam is tarah laee jaeygi ke uski sattar hazar lagaam hongi aur har lagaam key sath sattar hazar farishtey usey khinch rahey hongey.'' Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi kehtey hain : Sory ney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai.
2574,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din jahannam sey eik gardan niklegi uski do aankhen hongi jo dekhengi, do kaan hongey jo sunengey aur eik zaban hogi jo boleygi, wo kaheygi : mujhey teen logon par muqarrar kiya gaya hai : har sarkash zalim par, har us aadmi par jo Allah key siwa kisi doosrey ko pukarta ho, aur mujassama bananey walon par.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz logon ney ye hadees « an Aamash an Atiyaa an abi Saeed an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam» ki sanad sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 4- Ash-as bin sawar ney bhi « an Atiya an abi Saeed Al Khudri an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
2575,"Utba bin Ghazawaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamarey is Basra key member par bayan kiya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar eik bada bhari pathar jahannam key kinare sey dala jaey to wo sattar baras tak is mein girta jaaeyga phir bhi uski tahiya tak nahin pahunchega. Utba kehtey hain : umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : jahannam ko kasrat se yad karo, isliye ke uski garmi bahut sakht hai. uski gahraai bahut ziyada hai aur iskey aankdey lohey key hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hum Utba bin Ghazawaan sey Hasan Basri ka samaa (sun'na), nahin jantey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) key ehade khilaafat mein Utba bin Ghazawaan (Raziallahu anhu) Basra aaye they, aur Hasan Basri ki wiladat us waqt hui jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) key ehade khilaafat key do saal baqi they."
2576,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(Saood) jahannam ka eik pahad hai, is par kafir sattar saal mein chadheyga aur itney hi saal mein nichey gireyga aur ye azab usey hamesha hota rahega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf ibne-Lahiaa ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain."
2577,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kafir key chamdey ki motaai bayaalees gaz hogi, uski daadh uhad pahad jaisi hogi aur jahannam mein uskey bethney ki jagah itni hogi jitna Makka aur Madina key darmiyan ka fasla.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Aamash ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2578,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din kafir ki daadh uhad pahad jaisi hogi, uski raan baizaa (pahad) jaisi hogi aur jahannam key andar uskey bethney ki jagah teen meel ki masafat key barabar hogi jis tarah rabza ki doori hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- (مثل الربذة)  ka matlab hai ke jis tarah rabza pahad Madina sey door hai, rabza aur baizaa uhad ki tarah do pahad hain."
2579,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kafir ki daadh uhad jaisi hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2580,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kafir apni zaban ko eik ya do Farsakh tak ghasiteyga aur log isey rondengey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Fazal bin Yazeed Koofi hain, in sey kaee hadees ke Aaimma ney riwayat ki hai. 3- Abul Makhariq ghair maroof Raavi hain."
2581,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Allah Taala key qol « كالمهل » key barey mein farmaya : ''wo pani talchat ki tarah hoga jab usey (kafir) apney munh key qarib kerega to uskey chehrey ki khaal is mein gir jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees hum sirf Rushdain bin Saad ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Rushdain key barey mein kalam kiya gaya hai."
2582,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahannamiyon key sar par « ماء حمیم » (garm pani) undelaa jaeyga to wo (badan mein) saraayat kar jaeyga yahan tak ke uskey pet tak ja pahunchega aur uskey pet key andar jo kuchh hai usey kaateyga yahan tak ke uskey pairon (yani peeth) sey nikal jaaeyga. yehi wo «صہر» hai (jis ka zikr Quran mein aaya hai) phir isi tarah lota diya jaeyga jis tarah tha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2583,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala key is qol  ويسقى من ماء صديد يتجرعه ( Ibrahim : 16) key barey mein farmaya : '' « صديد » ( peep ( uskey munh key qarib ki jaeygi to usey napasand kerega jab usey aur qarib kya jaeyga to uska chehra bhun jaeyga aur uskey sar ki khaal gir jaeygi aur jab usey piyega to uski aant kat jaeygi yahan tak ke uskey peeth sey nikal jaeygi . Allah Taala farmata hai « وسقوا ماء حميما فقطع أمعاءهم » '' wo « ماء حمیم » ( garm pani ( palaey jaeyngey to wo un ki aanton ko kaat dega '' ( Sura Muhammad : 15) aur Allah Taala farmata hai « وإن يستغيثوا يغاثوا بماء كالمهل يشوي الوجوه بئس الشراب » '' aur agar wo fariyad kerengey to un ki fariyadrasi aisey pani sey ki jaeygi jo talchat ki tarah hoga chehrey ko bhoon dega aur wo nihayat bura mashrub hai'' ( Kahaf : 29 (Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- isi tarah Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney bhi sanad mein عن عبيد الله بن بسر kaha hai aur hum Ubedullah bin Basar ko sirf isi hadees mein jantey hain, 3- Safwan bin umr ney Abdullah bin Basar sey jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sabab hain, eik dusri hadees riwayat ki hai, Abdullah bin Basar key eik bhai hain jinhonney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suni hai aur unki eik behan ney bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadees suni hai. jis Ubedullah bin Basar sey Safwan bin Amr ney ye hadees riwayat ki hai, ye Sabab nahin hain koi doosrey aadmi hain."
2584,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' « كالمهل » yani talchat ki tarah hoga jab usey ( jahannami) apney qarib kerega to uskey chehrey ki khaal is mein gir jaeygi ''.
2585,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye aayat padhi اتقوا الله حق تقاته wala تموتن إلا وأنتم مسلمون ''tum Allah sey darney ki tarah daro aur musalman hi rehtey huye maro '' (Aale-Imran : 102) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar «Zaqqum» thoohad ka eik qatra bhi duniya ki zamin mein tapka diya jaey to duniya walon ki maeeshat bigad jaey, bhala us aadmi ka kya hoga jiski ghiza hi « zaqqum » ho . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2586,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jahannamiyon par bhook musallat kar di jaeygi aur ye azab key barabar ho jaeygi jis sey wo dochaar hongey, lihaza wo fariyad kerengey to unki fariyadrasi « ضريع » ( khaardaar paudey) key khaney sey ki jaeygi jo na unhen mota kerega aur na unki bhook khatam kerega, phir wo dobara khaney ki fariyad kerengey to unki fariyadrasi galey mein atakney waley khaney sey ki jaeygi, phir wo yad kerengey ke duniya mein atkey huye niwaley ko pani key zariey nigaltey they, chunanche wo pani ki fariyad kerengey aur unki fariyadrasi « حميم » ( jahannamiyon key mawad) sey ki jaeygi jo lohey key bartanon mein diya jaeyga jab mawad unkey chehron sey qarib hoga to unkey chehron ko bhoon dalega aur jab unkey pet mein jaeyga to unkey pet key andar jo kuch hai usey kaat dalega, wo kahengey : jahannam key darogha ko bulaao, darogha kahengey : kya tumharey paas Rasool roshan dalaeyl key sath nahin gaey they? wo kahengey : kyon nahin, darogha kahengey : pukartey raho , kafiron ki pukar bekar hi jaeygi ''. aap ney farmaya : '' jahannami kahengey : Malik ko bulaao aur kahengey : aey Malik ! chahiye ke tera rab hamara faisla kar dey ( hamen maut dedey ( '' , aap ney farmaya : '' in ko Malik jawab dega : tum log ( hamesha key liye ( isi mein rehney waley ho ''. Aamash kehtey hain : mujh sey bayan kya gaya ke un ki pukar aur Malik key jawab main eik hazar saal ka waqfa hoga, aap ney farmaya : '' jahannami kahengey : apney rab ko pukaro isliye ke tumharey rab sey behtar koi nahin hai, wo kahengey : aey hamarey rab! hamarey ooper shaqaawat ghalib aa gaee thi aur hum gumrah log they, aey hamarey rab ! hamen us sey nikal dey agar hum phir wesa hi kerengey to zalim hongey. aap ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala unhen jawab dega : phitkar ho tum par usi mein padey raho aur mujh sey baat na karo'', aap ney farmaya : ''us waqt wo har khair sey mehroom ho jaeyngey aur us waqt gadhey ki tarah renkney lagengey aur hasrat o halakat mein giraftar hongey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman ( Darmi ( kehtey hain : log is hadees ko marfooan nahin riwayat kartey hain, 2- hum is hadees ko sirf عن الأعمش an شمر بن عطية an شهر بن حوشب an أم الدرداء an أبي الدرداء ki sanad sey jantey hain jo abu-Darda ka apna qol hai, marfoo hadees nahin hai."
2587,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us aayate-karima « وهم فيها كالحون » '' kafir jahannam key andar bad shakal hongey '' ( al-Mominun 104) key barey mein farmaya : '' unkey chehron ko aag jhulas deygi to unkey ooper ka hont sikud kar bech sar tak pahunch jaeyga aur nichey ka hont latak kar naaf sey ja lagega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2588,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar uskey barabar eik tukda (aur aap ney apney sar ki taraf ishara kya ( aasman sey zamin ki taraf jo paanch so saal ki masafat hai, chhoda jaey to zamin par raat sey pehley pahunch jaeyga aur agar wohi tukda zanjeer (jis ka zikr) Quran mein aaya hai : « ثم في سلسلة ذرعها سبعون ذراعا فاسلكوه » ( الحاقة : ۳۲ ( key sar sey chhoda jaey to us zanjeer ki jad ya uski tahiya tak pahunchney sey pehley chaalis saal raat aur din key guzar jaeyn ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad Hasan sahih hai, 2- Saeed bin Yazeed Misri hain. un sey Les bin Saad aur kaee aimma ney hadees riwayat ki hai."
2589,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumhari ( duniya ki) aag jisey tum jalaatey ho jahannam ki aag key sattar hisson mein sey eik tukda ( hissey ( hai'' , logon ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! agar yehi aag rehti to kafi hoti, aap ney farmaya : ''wo us sey unhattar hissey badhi hui hai, har hissey ki garmi usi aag ki tarah hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2590,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumhari ye aag jahannam ki aag key sattar hisson mein sey eik hissa hai, uskey har hissey ki garmi isi tarah hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees abu-Saeed ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
2591,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahannam ki aag eik hazar saal dehkaai gaee yahan tak ke surkh ho gaee, phir eik hazar saal dehkaai gaee yahan tak ke safed ho gaee , phir eik hazar saal dehkaai gaee yahan tak ke siyah ho gaee, ab wo siyah hai aur taareek hai ''."
2592,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jahannam ney apney rab sey shikayat ki ke mera baaz hissa baaz hissey ko khaye ja raha hai lihaza Allah Taala ney uskey liye do sansein muqarrar kar din : eik saans garmi mein aur eik saans jadey mein, jahannam key jadey ki saans sey sakht sardi padti hai. aur uski garmi ki saans sey lo chalti hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey ye hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri sanad sey bhi marvi hai, 3- mufazzal bin Saleh muhaddeseen key nazdik koi qawi hafizey waley nahin hain."
2593,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jahannam sey niklega (Shoba ney apni riwayat mein kaha hai : (Allah taala kaheyga , usey jahannam sey nikal lo) jisney  لا إلٰہ إلا اللہ kaha aur uskey dil main eik jo key dana key barabar bhalai thi, usey jahannam sey nikalo jisney  لا إلٰہ إلا اللہ kaha, aur uskey dil mein gehun key daney key barabar bhalai thi, usey jahannam sey nikalo jisney  لا إلٰہ إلا اللہ  kaha uskey dil mein raai key dana key barabar bhalai thi. (Shoba ney kaha hai : juwar key barabar bhalai thi)''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir, abu Saeed Khudri aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2594,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala kaheyga : usey jahannam sey nikal lo jisney eik din bhi mujhey yad kya ya eik maqam par bhi mujh sey dara''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2595,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahannam sey sab sey aakhir mein nikalney waley aadmi ko main janta hun, wo aisa aadmi hoga jo peeth key bal chaltey huye niklega aur arz karega : aey merey rab ! log jannat ki tamam jagah ley chukey hongey.''  aap ney farmaya : ''us sey kaha jaeyga : chalo jannat mein dakhil ho jaao.'' aap ney farmaya : ''wo dakhil honey key liye jaeyga (jannat ko is haal mein) paeyga ke log tamam jagah ley chukey hain, wo wapis aa kar arz kerega : aey merey rab ! log tamam jagah ley chukey hain? !''  aap ney farmaya : ''us sey kaha jaeyga : kya wo din yad hain jin mein (duniya key andar) they?'' wo kaheyga : haan , us sey kaha jaeyga : ''aarzu karo''  aap ney farmaya : ''wo aarzu kerega, us sey kaha jaeyga : tumharey liye wo tamam cheezen jiski tum ney aarzu ki hai aur duniya key das guna hai.'' aap ney farmaya : ''wo kaheyga : (aey Bari Taala ! (aap mazaq kar rahey hain halanke aap Malik hain.''  ibne-Masood kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hanstey dekha yahan tak key aap key andruni key daant nazar aaney lagey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2596,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jahannam sey sab sey aakhir mein nikalney aur jannat mein sab sey aakhir mein dakhil honey waley aadmi ko main janta hun, eik aadmi ko laya jaeyga aur Allah Taala (farishton sey) kahega : is sey uskey chhotey chhotey gunahon key barey mein poochho aur uskey badey gunahon ko chupa do , us sey kaha jaeyga : tum ney falan falan din aisey aisey gunah kiye they, tum ney falan falan din aisey aisey gunah kiye they? '' , aap ney farmaya : '' us sey kaha jaeyga : tumharey har gunah key badley eik neki hai ''. aap ney farmaya : '' wo arz kerega : aey merey rab ! mainey kuch aisey bhi gunah kiye they jisey yahan nahin dekh raha hun ''. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hanstey huye dekha yahan tak key aap key andruni daant nazar aaney lagey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2597,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ek khuda ko maanney walon mein sey kuch log jahannam mein azab diye jaeyngey, yahan tak ke koila ho jaeyngey, phir un par rehmate-Ilaahi saya-figan hogi to wo nikaaley jaeyngey aur jannat key darwazey par dal diye jaeyngey''. aap ney farmaya : ''jannati un par pani chhidkengey to wo wesay hi ugeingey jaisey sailab ki mittiyon mein dana ugta hai, phir wo jannat mein dakhil hongey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye dusri sanad sey bhi Jabir sey marvi hai."
2598,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahannam sey wo aadmi niklega jiskey dil mein zarra barabar eman hoga, abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : jis ko shak ho wo ye aayat padhey إن الله لا يظلم مثقال ذرة '' Allah zarra barabar bhi zulm nahin karta hai'' (Nisa : 40) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2599,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahannam mein dakhil honey walon mein sey do aadmiyon ki cheekh buland hogi.'' Shaan wala Rab kaheyga : in dono ko nikalo , jab unhen nikala jaeyga to Allah Taala un sey puchheyga : tumhari cheekh kyon buland ho rahi hai? wo dono arz karengey : hamney aisa is wajeh sey kiya taake to hum par reham kar. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tum dono key liye hamari rehmat yehi hai ke tum jaao aur apney aap ko usi jagah jahannam mein dal do jahan pehley they. wo dono chalen gey un mein sey eik apney aap ko jahannam mein dal dega to Allah Taala uskey liye jahannam ko thanda aur salamti wali bana dega aur doosra khada rahega aur apney aap ko nahin daleyga. us sey Shaan wala Rab puchheyga : tumhen jahannam mein apney aap ko dalney sey kis chiz ney roka? jaisey tumharey sathi ney apney aap ko dala? wo arz kerega : aey merey rab ! mujhey ummid hai ke to jahannam sey nikalney key baad is mein dobara nahin dakhil kerega, us sey Rab taala kaheyga : tumharey liye teri tamanna puri ki ja rahi hai, phir wo dono Allah ki rehmat sey jannat mein dakhil hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ki sanad zaeef hai, isliye ke ye Rushdain bin Saad key wastey sey marvi hai, aur Rushdain bin Saad muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, aur Rushdain Abdur-Rehman bin Anam sey riwayat kartey hain, ye ibne Anam Afriqi hain aur Afriqi bhi muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain."
2600,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat ki eik jamaat meri shafaat key sabab jahannam sey niklegi unka naam jahannami rakha jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2601,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney jahannam jaisi koi chiz nahin dekhi jis sey bhagney waley sau rahey hain aur jannat jaisi koi chiz nahin dekhi jis key talab karney waley sau rahey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is ko hum sirf Yahya bin Ubedullah ki sanad sey jantey hain aur Yahya bin Ubedullah aksar muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, unkey barey mein Shoba ney kalam kiya hai. Yahya bin Ubedullah key dada ka naam Mohab hai aur wo Madni hain."
2602,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney jannat mein jhaankaa to dekha ke aksar jannati faqeer  hain aur jahannam mein jhaankaa to dekha ke aksar jahannami aurten hain.''
2603,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney jahannam mein jhaankaa to dekha ke aksar jahannami aurten hain aur jannat mein jhaankaa to dekha ke aksar jannati faqeer hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Auf ney sanad bayan kartey huye is tarah kaha hai : (عن أبي رجاء an عمران بن حصين) aur Ayub ney kaha : (عن أبي رجاء an ابن عباس), ‏‏‏‏dono sanadon mein koi kalam nahin hai. is baat ka ehtimaal hai ke abu-Rijaa ney Imran bin Husain aur ibne-Abbas dono sey suna ho, Auf key ilawa doosrey logon ney bhi ye hadees abu-Rijaa key wastey sey Imran bin Husain sey riwayat ki hai."
2604,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din sab sey halka azab wala wo jahannami hoga jis key talwey mein do angaarey hongey jin sey uska dimagh khol raha hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib, Abu Saeed Khudri aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
2605,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''kya main tumhen jannatiyon key barey mein na bata dun? har kamzor haal aadmi jisey log haqeer samjhen agar wo Allah ki qism khaye to Allah usey puri kar dey. kya main tumhen jahannamiyon key barey mein na bata dun? har sarkash , bakheel aur mutakabbir (jahannam mein jaeyga)."" Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
